name: Alien in the Void
description:
Ever wonder what life may look like on other planets?

I often wonder, if other forms of life have bodies like we do, would they be flat? or would they be spherical? 

Perhaps, some of them are just blobs of a sort of mass with a few sensory devices sticking out of them. Do they possess a skeleton, muscular system and a skin? Are they able to see, hear and touch? Do they breathe? 

No one can speculate anything close to what could be out there since out there is itself an unknown. That's how bizarre and unfamiliar our imagination is about anything outside of our current experience.

Digital Painting
2048x2048 Pixels

2016
